  "page": "Huntsman",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Huntsman</b> can refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Mad_Huntsman\" title=\"Mad Huntsman\">Mad Huntsman</a>, a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_Banners\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brotherhood without Banners\">Brotherhood without Banners</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harle_the_Huntsman\" title=\"Harle the Huntsman\">Harle the Huntsman</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Wildling\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildling\">wildling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Bolton\" title=\"Rogar Bolton\">Rogar Bolton</a>, known as <i>Rogar the Huntsman</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Corlos\" title=\"Corlos\">Corlos</a>, identified only as \"the huntsman\" in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>'s Histories &amp; Lore featurettes.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Huntsman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Harlon_the_Hunter\" title=\"Harlon the Hunter\">Harlon the Hunter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hunt\" title=\"House Hunt\">House Hunt</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hunter\" title=\"House Hunter\">House Hunter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarly\" title=\"House Tarly\">House Tarly</a>, whose coat of arms is a striding huntsman</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403124330\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 12/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 28/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argume